							<label>Includes</label>
							<ul>
								<li>
									500 Transection/2000 Token size <a
										title="1 World aprrox equal to 4 token">*</a
									>
								</li>
								<li>Experience any bot</li>
								<li>You can create one bot</li>
								<li>Web bot</li>
								<li>100 Notifier by any channel</li>
							</ul>
							<div class="button-wrapper">
								<a class="button">Go for free</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
						<div class="price-section">
							<h3 class="grad-3">Family</h3>
							<p>Experience free for all of your message, We will handle it</p>
							<h1>8.99$</h1>
							<label>Includes</label>
							<ul>
								<li>
									500 Transection/2000 Token size <a
